The paper proposes a method for active learning with noisy labeled data, which is a common problem in machine learning. The paper specifically focuses on image datasets, which suggests that it could fall under computer vision (cs.CV). The use of quality models and oracle queries also suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions the use of uncertainty measures, which is a common topic in information retrieval (cs.IR) and data science (cs.DS).
